vlc: vlc (VideoLAN Media Player)
vlc: 
vlc: VLC media player is a highly portable multimedia player for various 
vlc: audio and video formats such as MPEG-1, MPEG-2, MPEG-4, DivX, mp3,
vlc: and ogg, as well as DVDs, VCDs, and various streaming protocols. It 
vlc: can also be used as a server to stream in unicast or multicast in 
vlc: IPv4 or IPv6 on a high-bandwidth network.
